categories: Category:Members of the Spice Runners of Kijimi

nodes.text: Vibbo was a thug who worked with the spicerunner gang known as the Spice Runners of Kijimi, alongside Vicii. The two thugs accompanied the Spice Runners' leader, Zorii Bliss, to confront Poe Dameron, Resistance member and former Spice Runner who returned to Kijimi on a mission. Rey quickly intercepted the thugs, knocking them unconscious. The two thugs were taken back to the Spice Runners' den, and Vibbo woke up unable to remember returning there. The Spice Runners were later forced to escape the First Order, and Vibbo planned to hide. Shortly afterward, Kijimi was destroyed by the Derriphan, a Star Destroyer of the Final Order.
